Best of the Bangles is a single disc compilation album by Bangles which was released on the 31 May 1999 on the Columbia label containing 18 songs. Best of the Bangles serves as yet another great introduction to the group and a fine place to revel in nostalgia on the late 80s early 90s. Some of their classic songs are contained in this release including their biggest hits, Manic Monday, Eternal Flame and Walk Like An Egyptian.
